						Stop Juggling Multiple Websites {"for"} Basic Tasks
					</h2>
					<p class="text-lg text-black/70">
						Most developers waste time switching between different tool websites. 
						We solved this by building everything you need in one place.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="grid gap-8 grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
				<!-- Problem/Solution Cards -->
				<div class="backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/40 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/50 p-8 shadow-xl">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 text-red-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
